cohortName: [PL 4163261001] Malignant tumor of prostate referent concept incident cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants with >=365d prior observation
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (4163261) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 4163261002] Malignant tumor of prostate referent concept prevalent cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (4163261) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 4163261003] Malignant tumor of prostate incident cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants excluding secondary cancers, in males, excluding prior other cancers and H/O prostate cancer with >=365d prior observation
logicDescription: Primary prostate cancer at first diagnosis, males only, excluding prior cancer (except non-melanoma skin cancer) and excluding h/o prostate cancer.
